"current pattern (remember that filling a pattern is always relative to the "
"grid resolution set) and finally <quote><emphasis role=\"bold\">Randomize "
"velocity</emphasis></quote> automatically apply a pseudo-random velocity to "
"each note of that instrument in the pattern. The more velocity you set on "
