#: manual.docbook:1052(para)
msgid ""
"You can save your favorite patterns in the sound library by right clicking "
"the title of the pattern in the song editor, and selecting <guimenuitem>Save "
"Pattern</guimenuitem>. It will appear in the Sound Library underneath "
"<guilabel>Patterns</guilabel> and the category that you assigned to the "
